 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the videographer is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the engineercher##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the videographer##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the fan of disco is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person eating strawberry and the fan of reggae##2
14. the engineercher is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the nurse##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the person driving the ship and the person eating artichoke##2

